      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical option for someone seeking dependable basic transportation at a very accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a value-focused buyer, but it still offers solid everyday usefulness, a straightforward ownership proposition, and excellent upside for the right driver or project-minded shopper. An honest, affordable opportunity backed by a dealership you can buy from with confidence.",
