    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without the big price tag? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a genuine, budget-friendly option with lots of practical value for someone who wants simple transportation or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s been represented honestly and priced to reflect that, making it a great chance to get into a car for sensible money. If you want something straightforward, approachable, and worth a look, this could be the one.",
