    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong mechanical foundation and plenty of upside for the next owner. The engine fires up willingly, pulls through the rev range with good character, and the drivetrain feels like a worthwhile base for a budget build, commuter revival, or weekend wrenching project. It shows its age cosmetically and will need attention in a few areas, but that also means you can get into it at an accessible price point without paying for someone else\u2019s half-finished vision. Great candidate for an enthusiast who appreciates a usable platform with honest wear and room to improve.",
      "price": 6950.0,
