      "description": "This car has the kind of lived-in character you can\u2019t fake\u2014an honest, road-tested machine with plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s the sort of vehicle that appeals to someone who sees possibility: a dependable runabout, a practical spare, or a hands-on project with real charm. The body and cabin carry the marks of a life well traveled, but that only adds to its no-nonsense personality. If you want inexpensive wheels with grit, presence, and room to make it your own, this one is worth a look.",
